,"sicilia","sicily","museo archeologico regionale paolo orsi","latin",[],{"title":318,"body":319,"divs":320,"editions":345,"images":355,"handnote":361},"ISic000632. I.Sicily inscription 000632","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Salvo d(omino) n(ostro) \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Fl(avius) 𐆌 Gelasius Busiris v(ir) c̣(larissimus) [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>praetorium sine ullius [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>tot diebus quibus alli mensibuṣ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>SALVODN\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>FL𐆌GELASIUSBUSIRISV.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>PRAETORIUMSINEULLIUS[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>TOTDIEBUSQUIBUSALLIMENSIBU.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000632_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\" src=\"ISic000632_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000632.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\" src=\"ISic000632-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: F̣[l(avio) Valentiniano (?) Aug(usto)]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [cons(ularis) p(rovinciae) S(iciliae)]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [damno]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [restituit]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Manganaro suggests restoring either Valentinian III (424-455 CE) or Theodosius II (402-405 CE); Ferrua argued rather for later 5th or even 6th century CE. For Busiris, see PLRE II.243-4. In part it depends upon the possible date range of the use of the formula Salvo domino nostra (attested from the Constantinian period onwards, but more common from the Theodosian period), and also the addressing of a single emperor. \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000652\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000652\u003C/a> was found in close proximity.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1980.0512 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1946.0207 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Cultrera NSA 1940 218-219 fig.27 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1941 157-158 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mazzarino 1942-1943 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Chastagnol 1963 371 n.26 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Wilson 1990 333 n.34 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1993 579-582 fig.9 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Broken bar A, D tending to square, lunate E, G with trailing tail, closed P and R. Use of a sinusoid form interpunct after FL in line 2.\u003C/p> Line 1  62  Line 2  60-78  Line 3  51-62  Line 4  45-48  Interlineation line 1 to 2  15-25  Interlineation line 2 to 3  22-30  Interlineation line 3 to 4  32-40  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[321,324,327,330,333,336,339,342],{"id":322,"html":323},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Salvo d(omino) n(ostro) \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Fl(avius) 𐆌 Gelasius Busiris v(ir) c̣(larissimus) [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>praetorium sine ullius [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>tot diebus quibus alli mensibuṣ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>SALVODN\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>FL𐆌GELASIUSBUSIRISV.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>PRAETORIUMSINEULLIUS[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>TOTDIEBUSQUIBUSALLIMENSIBU.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":325,"html":326},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000632_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\" src=\"ISic000632_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000632.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\" src=\"ISic000632-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":328,"html":329},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: F̣[l(avio) Valentiniano (?) Aug(usto)]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [cons(ularis) p(rovinciae) S(iciliae)]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [damno]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: [restituit]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":331,"html":332},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":334,"html":335},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Manganaro suggests restoring either Valentinian III (424-455 CE) or Theodosius II (402-405 CE); Ferrua argued rather for later 5th or even 6th century CE. For Busiris, see PLRE II.243-4. In part it depends upon the possible date range of the use of the formula Salvo domino nostra (attested from the Constantinian period onwards, but more common from the Theodosian period), and also the addressing of a single emperor. \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000652\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000652\u003C/a> was found in close proximity.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":337,"html":338},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1980.0512 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1946.0207 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Cultrera NSA 1940 218-219 fig.27 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1941 157-158 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mazzarino 1942-1943 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Chastagnol 1963 371 n.26 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Wilson 1990 333 n.34 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1993 579-582 fig.9 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":340,"html":341},"handnote","\u003Cp>Broken bar A, D tending to square, lunate E, G with trailing tail, closed P and R. Use of a sinusoid form interpunct after FL in line 2.\u003C/p> Line 1  62  Line 2  60-78  Line 3  51-62  Line 4  45-48  Interlineation line 1 to 2  15-25  Interlineation line 2 to 3  22-30  Interlineation line 3 to 4  32-40  ",{"id":343,"html":344},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[346,348,351,352],{"html":347},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2018-03-15",{"id":349,"lang":159,"html":350},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Salvo d(omino) n(ostro) \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Fl(avius) 𐆌 Gelasius Busiris v(ir) c̣(larissimus) [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>praetorium sine ullius [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>tot diebus quibus alli mensibuṣ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":347},{"id":353,"lang":159,"html":354},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>SALVODN\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>FL𐆌GELASIUSBUSIRISV.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>PRAETORIUMSINEULLIUS[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>TOTDIEBUSQUIBUSALLIMENSIBU.[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",[356,358],{"image":135,"thumb":357,"title":138},"ISic000632_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":359,"thumb":360,"title":138},"ISic000632.jpg","ISic000632-thumb.jpg",[362],{"html":57},"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>I.Sicily inscription 000632\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n\t   \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>conversion to EpiDoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n\t    \u003CrespStmt>\n     \t       \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n     \t       \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n \t   \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic000632\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\">175845\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\">073621\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\">15100066\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000632\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"DOI\" when=\"2020-12-17\">10.5281/zenodo.4338127\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Siracusa\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/097\">Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\">50739\u003C/idno>\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"la\">Latin\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>Large limestone block. Intact front, left, and partly on top and at resar. The right side is lost and the upper surface is uneven, very worn, and clearly missing some material. A piece is missing rear right.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.limestone\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html\">limestone\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.block\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html\">block\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">36\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">90\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">60\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.damaged\"/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>The front face preserves four lines of Latin text, with a clear margin on the left, loss to the upper right of line 1, and from the right end of all four lines. A deep circular hole has been drilled into the middle of line 4, which however the letters appear to be engraved around.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.incomplete\"/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>Broken bar A, D tending to square, lunate E, G with trailing tail, closed P and R. Use of a sinusoid form interpunct after FL in line 2.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"62\" atMost=\"62\">62\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line2\">Line 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"60\" atMost=\"78\">60-78\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line3\" to=\"line3\">Line 3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"51\" atMost=\"62\">51-62\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line4\" to=\"line4\">Line 4\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"45\" atMost=\"48\">45-48\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"15\" atMost=\"25\">15-25\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line3\">Interlineation line 2 to 3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"22\" atMost=\"30\">22-30\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line3\" to=\"line4\">Interlineation line 3 to 4\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"32\" atMost=\"40\">32-40\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462503\">Syracusae\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2523083\">Siracusa\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>37.08415, 15.27628\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0401\" notAfter-custom=\"0550\" evidence=\"lettering titulature\">5th or early 6th century CE\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\" notBefore=\"1934\" notAfter=\"1936\">Found during works to open Via del Littorio on Ortygia, between 1934 and 1936; one of a number of unstratified finds (apparently in secondary deposition, reused as building material) in the area of Largo Antonello Gagini, formerly Largo XXVIII Ottobre\u003Cgeo>37.0629811,15.2921563\u003C/geo>. Now in storage in the Museo Archeologico Regionale di Siracusa.\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- location of Largo Antonello Gagini -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\" resp=\"#JP\" xml:id=\"autopsy\">Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.building\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/86.html\">building\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2017-01-20\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag checked the EpiDoc and added an image\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-03\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from autopsy notes\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000632_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000632.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-03-15\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#JP\" source=\"#autopsy\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>Salvo \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>omino\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>n\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ostro\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cgap reason=\"illegible\" unit=\"character\" quantity=\"1\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" unit=\"character\" extent=\"unknown\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Fl\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>avius\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#sinusoid\">&#65932;\u003C/g> Gelasius Busiris \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>v\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ir\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>\u003Cunclear>c\u003C/unclear>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>larissimus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>praetorium sine ullius \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>tot diebus quibus alli mensibu\u003Cunclear>s\u003C/unclear> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text from autopsy\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"1\">\u003Cnote>Manganaro: \u003Cunclear>F\u003C/unclear>[l(avio) Valentiniano (?) Aug(usto)]\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\u003Cnote>Manganaro: [cons(ularis) p(rovinciae) S(iciliae)]\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"3\">\u003Cnote>Manganaro: [damno]\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"4\">\u003Cnote>Manganaro: [restituit]\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Manganaro suggests restoring either Valentinian III (424-455 CE) or Theodosius II (402-405 CE); Ferrua argued rather for later 5th or even 6th century CE. For Busiris, see PLRE II.243-4. In part it depends upon the possible date range of the use of the formula Salvo domino nostra (attested from the Constantinian period onwards, but more common from the Theodosian period), and also the addressing of a single emperor. \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000652\">ISic000652\u003C/ref> was found in close proximity.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1980.0512\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1946.0207\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Cultrera\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1940\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>218-219 fig.27\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mazzarino\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1942-1943\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/263VAK8N\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002785\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Chastagnol\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1963\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>371 n.26\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EU46JFMA\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002078\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1941\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>157-158\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4HR4GXBX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Wilson\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1990\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>333 n.34\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VF9MMBI9\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1993\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>579-582 fig.9\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JBI7CI5R\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001827\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
